{"word":"ἀναλαμβάνω","slug":"ἀναλαμβάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀναλαμβάνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λαμβάνω\">λαμβάνω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘to cause movement in an upward direction’, <b><i>take up</i></b> of Jesus <b><a href='B:480 16:19'>Mk 16:19</a>; <a href='B:510 1:2'>Ac 1:2</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; <b><a href='B:610 3:16'>1 Ti 3:16</a>;</b> of a sheet <b><a href='B:510 10:16'>Ac 10:16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘to lift up in order to take along’, <b><i>take up, take along</i> <a href='B:510 7:43'>Ac 7:43</a>;</b> in military imagery<b> <a href='B:560 6:13'>Eph 6:13</a>, <a href='B:560 6:16'>16</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘to take someone with’, <b><i>pick up, get</i> <a href='B:510 23:31'>Ac 23:31</a>; <a href='B:620 4:11'>2 Ti 4:11</a>;</b> <i>take on board ship</i> <b><a href='B:510 20:13'>Ac 20:13</a>, <a href='B:510 20:14'>14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακύπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀναλημφθείς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}